            <li>Full condenser coil cleaning (reach-ins and prep tables)</li>
            <li>Evaporator fan blade cleaning — remove grease accumulation</li>
            <li>Door gasket replacement if any wear or separation detected</li>
            <li>Temperature controller calibration check</li>
